Jefferies to Buy Prudential Financial’s Bache Unit, WSJ Says

-- B y   C h r i s   P e t e r s o n
-- 
2011-04-07T04:08:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/jefferies-to-buy-prudential-financial-s-bache-unit-wsj-says.html
Jefferies Group Inc. (JEF)  is to buy
 Prudential Financial Inc. (PRU) ’s Bache commodities and financial
derivatives unit for about $400 million, the Wall Street Journal
reported, citing people familiar with the situation.  The deal, which would see the 400-person unit renamed
Jefferies Bache, may be announced as soon as today, the
newspaper said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Peterson at 
 cpeterson@bloomberg.net  